<subSubSection lastPageId="31" lastPageNumber="32" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="30.[151,1437,1620,2005]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">Chocolate brown. Median narrow stripe along crown, pronotum and mesoscutum brownish yellow, oblique stripe along anterolateral margin of crown brownish yellow, except extreme short lateral margin in front of eye. Face orange yellow more so along median carina and lateral areas frontoclypeus and clypellus, lorum and gena more yellowish, oblique thin line along dorsal margin dark brown. Thoracic pleura yellow, legs and sterna orange, setae on hind tibiae yellow. Forewing dark brown with basal 0.66 of costal margin broadly hyaline tinged with yellow, on angular spot beyond this hyaline area on outer apical cells, inner claval cell and all apical cells hyaline, latter traversed by transverse brown band.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="30.[151,1437,1620,2005]" lastBlockId="31.[151,1436,151,467]" lastPageId="31" lastPageNumber="32" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">
<emphasis box="[199,366,1871,1896]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">Male genitalia</emphasis>
. Pygofer with dorsal margin convex in posterior region, lobe posteriorly rounded with stout macrosetae along dorsal margin posteriorly. Subgenital plates narrowed distally with inner submarginal row of macrosetae and hair-like setae along outer margin. Connective and style as in generic description. Aedeagus with short dorsolateral lobe extending to basal 0.75 length, rather convex, shaft short anteriorly curved, ventral margin of aedeagus sinuate with angular projection, in posteroventral view broadest in middle. Segment X reaching apex of pygofer posteriorly and tubular.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="31.[151,1436,151,467]" pageId="31" pageNumber="32">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,381,223,248]" pageId="31" pageNumber="32">Measurements.</emphasis>
Male 
<quantity box="[458,547,223,248]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.2" pageId="31" pageNumber="32" unit="mm" value="5.2">5.2 mm</quantity>
long, head 1.0 mm wide across eyes and 
<quantity box="[1040,1129,224,248]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.1" pageId="31" pageNumber="32" unit="mm" value="1.1">1.1 mm</quantity>
wide across posterolateral angles of pronotum.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
